{"tid":1564083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府捉到和理非心態","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:31:03.000Z","uid":313312,"like":41,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4f89cead416394cbc14080c01592a041365509","tid":1564083,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"和理非已經可以參與既空間越黎越少。<br />\n<br />\n身邊既人唔敢上街遊行集會，而事實係有不反對通知書都可以夾硬中斷，好多和理非，行完返屋企機會都無。<br />\n<br />\n依家又無大台俾佢地造神，又唔似雨傘時和平理性非暴力係主流，冇哂精神依賴，突然有首歌俾佢地寄托，咪係咁造神<br />\n<br />\n依首歌其實同海闊天空既意義一樣用黎俾班人精神寄托。<br />\n<br />\n最慘係要迫全世界認同，唔認同就分化，就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話國歌多餘，依家係討論國歌階段？<br />\n退一萬步，係都制定法律先，幾時輪到國歌？<br />\n何況依家打緊杖。<br />\n<br />\n你話首歌可以凝聚大家，更加廢話，凝聚大家係本身首歌有冇共鳴，而唔係佢係咪國歌。<br />\n<br />\n唱依首歌同當年唱海闊天空其實都無分別，都係俾班左膠圍爐取暖，但問題你唔好迫人跟蹤，又叫人背，又要推上電台<br />\n<br />\n學左膠講，鐘意自己會背，唔洗係咁洗版，我知你地連上街既權利都冇左，係好慘，但唔好自己呃自己，唱歌有用，雨傘時候早有普選。<br />\n<br />\n自由唔係免費，世上沒快樂抗爭，當初點解政府會讓步，係因為有班人用血用淚用生命換返黎。<br />\n<br />\n唔好用首歌造神，返去正軌，記住強權只怕力量，唔係歌聲。<br />\n世上邊場革命唔係用力量贏返黎？"},{"pid":"2662a5243b5d006171bbf11df1c8c6df9fdd2cf5","tid":1564083,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86694b2bf6d32fb82e58fb3d033d9a407f568b3f","tid":1564083,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a0c5917568675933991fe2426acb21ea153a553f","tid":1564083,"uid":6363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"想點？<br />\n又想人圍狗屋？"},{"pid":"45d428411b4bdcb10b042d38ac7dffa29f882e2d","tid":1564083,"uid":306692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e14db662095cb5843ff1e4f7af3f409b62b3a78","tid":1564083,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0c5917568675933991fe2426acb21ea153a553f","tid":1564083,"uid":6363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"想點？<br />\n又想人圍狗屋？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"快閃行動"},{"pid":"6dd9c079e406bac83bd5a41161509d105a914611","tid":1564083,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"435f2efd98d851738a23b67ecae9fec64415172f","tid":1564083,"uid":57634,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分化撚P牌仔<br />\n<br />\n善用不推文回覆</span>"},{"pid":"e93b70edd12677968f687e80590c84af410443c2","tid":1564083,"uid":6363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"如果政府繼續唔畀遊行，<br />\n搵個星期六日去18 區商場，由下午2 點唱到夜晚9點。<br />\n到時商場所做唔到生意睇吓邊個傷<img src